name: NFFH - WorkingAnteater
description:
NFFH is an abbreviation for "Non-Fungible Fire Hydrant". This is a collaborative work with WorkingAnteater (@Tentomusi).

His objkts appearing here are:

#172893: Working anteater - Van Gogh style
#180458: Working anteater - Eugène Delacroix style
#164660: Moonlight
#175276: Found something
#190408: Working anteater - ninacrypto style
(from top left to bottom right)

Arikui san, thank you again for allowing me to include these beautiful works here!

Minted on 3rd August 2021.
